{"tid":1808221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有人同我介紹左個好有樂趣的交費方法","createTime":"2020-01-02T08:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T08:51:43.000Z","uid":167597,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b45daa32a7b515ef3ce7b4e28b0e05d6abf96a","tid":1808221,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"十分簡單，5分鐘學識。<br />\n你只需要一部電腦。<br />\n<br />\n首先，上Google 搵一種叫自動點擊的軟件，我就用mouse recorder<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟著，登入網上銀行，用自動點擊軟件錄製你一次交費的點擊過程。<br />\n<br />\n然後，軟件就可以不停重復幫你交費。<br />\n<br />\n我岩岩試左，交左200次。<br />\n我份人，消費交錢就最高興，次數愈多愈開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然要分享俾多d人，大家一齊高興！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n和理非行動"},{"pid":"2207beac958b41c17ad838ae177ab1db62d2ff34","tid":1808221,"uid":167597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"推，大家一齊高興下"},{"pid":"3c18c226347d6049c0ae53181dd463a433f4c71e","tid":1808221,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:39:05.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"f31bfa4980d6b95fb0becfe5718bcfdf68f43335","tid":1808221,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"幫手推下，唔該"},{"pid":"c6291d253ecb57661da89f4eee4bf16e626ffc68","tid":1808221,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1130ff66625bea005ca5bc052a414c06cbbfeca5","tid":1808221,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6175d968ac3463b3f9029a6f7e12bcae760a24","tid":1808221,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1130ff66625bea005ca5bc052a414c06cbbfeca5","tid":1808221,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐<img sr